                    <p>Write the function <m>f</m> as a set of ordered pairs.</p>
                    <instruction>Since it is a <em>set</em>, the answer should be in curly braces. Each ordered pair has a comma inside <em>and</em> the ordered pairs themselves should be separated by commas.</instruction>
                    <p><var name="$answer" evaluator="$evaluator" width="30" /></p>
